Healthcare Analytics

Project Overview:
This project analyzes healthcare patient data and predicts test results using Machine Learning.

Tools Used:
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Scikit-learn
- Streamlit
- Power BI
- SQL

Features:
- Data Cleaning
- Exploratory Data Analysis
- Feature Engineering
- Machine Learning Prediction
- Interactive Streamlit Application